text: Tomas Söderblom (born 4 April 1972) is a Finnish rower. He competed in the men's single sculls event at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Finnish male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Finland Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:People from Pargas
